*"Ostavite* mi nekoliko minuta da se spremim." (Leave me a few minutes to get ready.)

*"Molim vas da *ostavite* svoje komentare ispod." (Please leave your comments below.)

*"Ne možete da *ostavite* bez pažnje." (You can't leave it without attention.)

*"Oni su *ostavili* sve i otišli." (They left everything and went away.)

*"Gde ste *ostavili* svoj džeparac?" (Where did you leave your wallet?)

*"Ona je *ostavila* bebu kod bake." (She left the baby with her grandmother.)